{"title":"sql DISTINCT 命令简单使用","date":"2018-06-01T03:01:00.000Z","link":"post/116","categories":["DataBase"],"updated":"2019-04-27T13:26:25.430Z","content":"<p>在表中，可能会包含重复值。这并不成问题，不过，有时也许希望仅仅列出不同（distinct）的值。<br>关键词 DISTINCT 用于返回唯一不同的值。<br>其实就是求select记录中求唯一的值<br>多字段求distinct<br><figure class=\"highlight sql\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">select</span> <span class=\"keyword\">DISTINCT</span> a.* ,c.device_name <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> A</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n","prev":{"title":"jQuery post提交数据","link":"post/117"},"next":{"title":"简单的ajax请求加php逻辑处理","link":"post/113"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/116/"}